author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: J. Cole Announces 57-City ‘4 Your Eyez Only’ World Tour
text:
In support of his late-2016 album 4 Your Eyez Only , J. Cole will be embarking on a 57-city world tour, beginning June 1. The series of concerts kicks off in South Carolina, as Cole will then be making his way throughout North America, before heading across the pond to the UK. There will also be a mix of arena and theater dates in Europe, Australia and New Zealand as well.
American Express Card Members can go ahead and purchase tickets before the general public as of today, February 21, through Thursday, February 23. Tickets then go on sale to everyone else beginning Friday, February 24.
See below for the coinciding dates and locations for J. Cole’s upcoming 4 Your Eyez Only tour.
